[Detail]
符号入口：

- `Runnable`：`libs/core/langchain_core/runnables/base.py:125`
- `BaseChatModel`：`libs/core/langchain_core/language_models/chat_models.py:270`
- `BaseLanguageModel`：`libs/core/langchain_core/language_models/base.py:141`
- `BaseTool`：`libs/core/langchain_core/tools/base.py:405`
- `BaseRetriever`：`libs/core/langchain_core/retrievers.py:55`
- `VectorStore`：`libs/core/langchain_core/vectorstores/base.py:43`
- `BaseMessage`：`libs/core/langchain_core/messages/base.py:93`
- `Document`：`libs/core/langchain_core/documents/base.py:288`
- `create_agent`：`libs/langchain_v1/langchain/agents/factory.py:697`
- `ChatOpenAI`：`libs/partners/openai/langchain_openai/chat_models/base.py:2534`
- `TextSplitter`：`libs/text-splitters/langchain_text_splitters/base.py:44`
- `langchain-profiles refresh`：`libs/model-profiles/langchain_model_profiles/cli.py:255`

常用命令模式：

- 安装测试依赖：在目标包目录运行 `uv sync --group test`
- 单包单测：`uv run --group test pytest tests/unit_tests/...`
- lint：按包运行 `make lint` 或 `uv run --group lint ruff ...`
- typing：按包运行 `uv run --group lint mypy .`

